\par CODIGO-}{\cf1\lang9226 Objeto}{\b\cf1\lang9226 /CODIGO-}{\cf1\lang9226 Materia divisible e independiente}{\b\cf1\lang9226 /CODIGO-}{\cf1\lang9226 Divisi\'f3n del objeto de regulaci\'f3n}{\b\cf1\lang9226 /CODIGO-}{\cf1\lang9226 
